LightPainter is an experimental app to recreate the popular long exposure photography
otherwise known as Light Painting. 

Full source available at http://github.com/darksuiyoken/LightPainter



Simple Implementation
---------------------

1. Import the class

import com.designfission.effects.LightPainer;

2. Initialize the class (with camera width and height)

var lightPainter = new LightPainter(640,480);
lightPainter.init();

3. Methods

	=======================================
	lightPainter.startRecord();
	=======================================
	lightPainter.stopRecord();
	=======================================
	lightPainter.exportImage();		